  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  18 to 45 years old

          -  mild to moderate persistent asthma (GINA classification)

          -  stabilized asthma

          -  physical activity level between 5 and 11 (Baecke and coll, 1982)

          -  no contra-indication for physical training

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  cardiovascular pathology

          -  metabolic pathology

          -  traumatic pathology

          -  BMI≥30

          -  tobacco

          -  diabetes
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
